This is a couple of Web Forms that interact with a Bugzilla instalation.
It is quite specific in the problem it is addressing so it is probably not
Easily reusable for others but feel free to glean what you can from the various
Files that make up the app.

This app does require some non default PHP extentions
- php xmlrpc extention http://us.php.net/manual/en/book.xmlrpc.php
- php curl extention http://php.net/manual/en/book.curl.php
- php ldap extention http://us.php.net/manual/en/book.ldap.php
